# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. LIVE LOGS:
#    - logs/*/live/ is ALWAYS excluded
#    - This prevents accidentally committing real money transactions
#    - Live logs persist on host but never in Git
#
# 2. PAPER LOGS:
#    - Paper trading logs are SAFE to commit
#    - Useful for analysis, backtesting, and audit
#    - Can be excluded if they get too large (uncomment sections above)
#
# 3. OBSERVATION LOGS:
#    - Monitoring logs without trading
#    - Safe to commit
#    - India market observation runs 24/7
#
# 4. SECRETS:
#    - .env files contain API keys and MUST be excluded
#    - Use .env.example for documentation
#
